Ashdale.Description: Once a thriving community, now a war-torn ruin marking the destruction that befell the land of Cascadia.

Churrotown.Description: The most recent Cascadian development, headed by current leader churrolover16.

Skeleton Farm.Description: A converted Cascadian skeleton farm structured for wolves to level up alongside their humans.

Northeast Sea.Description: An ocean claim by tEM_fLAKs that goes all the way up to the northeast world border.

Pillager Outpost.Description: A converted pillager outpost owned by Cascadia.

Ice Spikes.Description: A historic preservation biome that features a magnificent collection of natural ice sculptures.

Edoras.Description: The mushroom city in Caladium, known for its massive cobblestone tower.

Caladium.Description: A beautiful kingdom located in the birch flower forest and mushroom island. Its capital city is Aster.

Cascadian Desert.Description: The northern deserts used by Cascadia.

Ejypt.Description: Ejypt's once peaceful and agrarian fields now lie in desolation and abandonment.

Spawn.Description: The server's spawn area: an intersection between forest plains, desert, ocean, and mesa.
